steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click Edit Buld Information on the side bar menu
Input the description 'This is a test description in the 'Description' field on the Edit Build Information page
Click on the 'Preview' button on the Edit Build Information page
Get Preview text on the Edit Build Information page
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
